title: LOOK (Japanese band) - Partial Discography + Lives + PVs
description:
== BIOGRAPHY ==

1985 to 1989 japanese band of pop and ballads. LOOK's best theme is "SHINING ON KIMI GA KANASHII". Vocal is "Tohru Suzuki", and the rest of the group are "Masashi Chizawa", "Harukichi Yamamoto", and "CHEEP Hiroishi" (deceased in March 2014). 

Name "LOOK" cames from a chocolate japanese, "LOOK a la mode". The group disolves in 1989, and Tohru Suzuki started with his solitaire carreer.

In 2008, Yasu, ex-vocalist from "Janne Da Arc", and actual vocal of "Acid Black Cherry" make a cover of "SHINING ON KIMI GA KANASHII".

== THIS TORRENT INCLUDES ==

* Partial Discography of LOOK: Albums "BOYS BE DREAMIN" and "LOOKIN WONDERLAND" completes!!.... Albums "WINGS" and "OVER-LOOK" incompletes. File: "Tracks for search and find.txt" included in "LOOK" main folder, contains the name of the tracks no included in "WINGS" and "OVER-LOOK" (because I can't find it). If you find it, please upload to you tube (MP3 TUBE ^^), or mail me to:

All singles are complete ^^!!


* Videos of LOOK: Various "LIVE" and "PV" videos from LOOK, in special, videos of "SHINING ON KIMI GA KANASHII".
